data.description: Buyers dream! $5000 in sellers concessions to further buy down the rate or to use towards closing costs. Introducing a stunning three-bedroom, two-bath home in a charming neighborhood in Port LaBelle. This NEW construction seamlessly combines modern elegance with practical functionality. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open concept living space that effortlessly connects the living room, dining area and kitchen. The entire home boasts an abundance of natural light, thanks to strategically placed windows and an especially charming feature, a large window in the kitchen. Granite countertops and beautiful white cabinets adorn this kitchen. The large primary bedroom has a spacious walk-in closet and en-suite bath to relax in. The backyard has plenty of space for a pool. This home won't last long.
